subject: Golf
United States Open (Golf)
lead_paragraph: If KellyAnn Callahan has her way, Tiger Woods will play the 10th hole of Winged Foot Golf Club in the United States Open, hop the short fence and meet her and her sister, Maggie, in the backyard for a play date.
